Spritz Technology, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 5:09 PM ET
Software

Company Overview of Spritz Technology, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Spritz Technology, Inc. develops a text-streaming technology. Its technology presents individual words at the reader’s comfortable speed, allowing them to read without having to move their eyes. The company’s technology is available on desktops, smartphones, and wearables, as well as supported in various languages in the United States and internationally. Its technology is also integrated in Websites and apps. The company serves online publishers, advertisers, content platforms, and device makers. Spritz Technology was founded in 2011 and is based in Wakefield, Massachusetts.


607 North AvenueSuite 12Wakefield, MA 01880United StatesFounded in 2011



Phone: 781-568-0871

www.spritzinc.com







