Baby Spritz, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 5:09 PM ET
Personal Products

Company Overview of Baby Spritz, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Baby Spritz, Inc. manufactures and markets baby sprays. It offers diaper rash and baby wipe alternative sprays. The company markets its product under Baby Spritz brand name. Baby Spritz is based in New Hempstead, New York.


5 Wayne RoadNew Hempstead, NY 10977United States



Phone: 877-277-7480

Fax: 845-364-9036

www.babyspritz.com







Key Executives for Baby Spritz, Inc.




Ms. Mindy Cohen


      	Founder
      








Mr. Michael Cohen


      	Director of Marketing
      





Compensation as of Fiscal Year 2017. 



