Spritz Technology, Inc.






Industry:
Computer Software 

Founded:
                    2012                

Type:
                    Privately Held                

Size:
                    11-50 Employees.                



Specialities:
                    Reading Technologies,
Wearables,
Mobile Devices,
Mobile Software,
Technology Licensing,
Research and Development                



Categories:
                    Wearables                



                    Spritz Inc. is a Boston-based start-up focused on text streaming technology and its integration into modern communication. The founders are serial entrepreneurs with extensive experience in developing and commercializing innovative technologies. We have assembled an international team of experts in reading methodologies and software engineering. Spritz offers a variety of licensing options for the integration with operating systems, applications, websites and wearables. 

Our Technology:

The time-consuming part in reading is the eye movement from word to word, which requires lots of space. With compact text streaming from Spritz, the eye does not have to move. This enables fast streaming which more comfortable and easier for the reader. Spritz’s patent-pending technology also can be integrated into photos, maps, videos and websites for more effective communication. This also creates more opportunities for advertising especially on mobile devices.                






 













